  <brief_title>Traumeel® S in Preventing and Treating Mucositis in Young Patients Undergoing Stem Cell Transplantation</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized Double Blind Placebo Controlled Clinical Trial to Assess the Efficacy of Traumeel® S (IND#66649) for the Prevention and Treatment of Mucositis in Children Undergoing Hematopoietic Stem Cell Transplantation</official_title>
